ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectAgreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of Quebec concerning the monitoring of water quality in Quebec
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment, on behalf of the Government of Canada, to enter into an AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of Quebec concerning the MONITORING OF WATER QUALITY IN QUEBEC for a period of five years, effective April 1, 2012 and ending on March 31, 2017.
